Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: uniflash
Version: 1.1
Summary: Reflash Logitech Unifying Receivers easily
Home-page: UNKNOWN
Author: athn
Author-email: jem@seethis.link
License: MIT
Description: Reflash Logitech Unifying Receivers easily
        
        Windows users please install libusb first. (Go to https://sourceforge.net/projects/libusb-win32/files/libusb-win32-releases/1.2.6.0, download libusb-win32-devel-filter-1.2.6.0.exe and install it)
        
        Usage: uniflash <command> [<args>]
        
        command is one of:
            icp         reset the unifying firmware into its bootloader mode
            reset       reset from the bootloader
            flash       when in icp mode flash the given hexfile
            info        print info about bootloader (nRF24LU1+)
            info_ti     print info about bootloader (CC2544)
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
